data.description: Motivated Seller! Port St John, updated and move in ready! Not only does this home have an adorable curb appeal, but it has no shortage of updates on the inside as well. Wood look tile throughout, updated 5.25'' baseboards, double pane windows, and updated kitchen and bathrooms. The kitchen has gray cabinetry with soft close drawers, quartz countertops, stainless steel single bowl sink, and newer stainless steel appliances. Both bathrooms are updated with new vanities, dual flush toilets, lighting, and the shower has been nicely tiled with subway tiles. The fenced in yard is perfect for pets, has 2 sheds for storage, and plenty of parking for your recreational vehicles. To top it all off it is concrete block, roof 2016, AC 2022, updated electrical panel, and 50 amp
